    public class ProblemCallable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.concurrent.Callable<com.alibaba.fastjson.JSONArray>
    Class ProblemCallable implements Callable.

    This Callable is used to get related problems for the corresponding entity name.

    Returns data in JSONArray, each object inside as follows. 

    
 {
     "qBody"   : < A string represent problem's statement, include choices >
     "qAnswer" : < A String represent problem's answer >
     "id"      : An integer, the problem's id
 }

    Note that the answer and the choices might in multiple kinds of forms
